{"tid":2515673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁唐青儀: 五四運動大學生為了保衛國家領土完整而走上街頭 與反修例事件走上街頭的年青人理念完全是背道而馳","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T06:56:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"836686a0eefa4119b8e342f0ad71b5de490e381d","tid":2515673,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"香港電台舉辦五四運動102周年升旗禮，活動籌委會召集人梁唐青儀說，當年大學生為了保衛國家領土完整而走上街頭，與前年本港反修例事件，走上街頭的年青人理念完全是背道而馳。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局局長徐英偉、廣播處長李百全、「世紀長征」系列活動籌委會召集人梁唐青儀出席儀式。<br />\n<br />\n十二個青少年制服團隊，以英式步操進場，包括聖若翰救傷隊少青團、青少年軍總會和童軍總會等<br />\n<br />\n女童軍首次擔任國旗升旗手，升旗隊總會則負責升區旗，並由學生宣讀五四宣言。<br />\n<br />\n籌委會召集人梁唐青儀稱，當年五四運動也是由大學生發起，希望青年人能學習五四運動，保家衛國的精神。<br />\n<br />\n「世紀長征」系列活動籌委會召集人梁唐青儀：「經過前年社會發生騷亂暴動事件，我認為要幫青年人，我覺得他們走出來，也是因為有一腔熱誠，但我想分享的是，102年前他們的先輩，也是大學生，他們也走上街頭，他們也有遊行示威，某程度上也有類似現今法律上的暴動行為，當時的青年人是要保障國家領土的完整，所以才走上街頭，似乎這些理念，與前年很多青年人走上街頭的理念完全是背道而馳。」<br />\n<br />\n協助升區旗的護旗手指，現今社會仍適用五四運動精神。<br />\n<br />\n護旗手黃卓賢：「現今社會最重要是有愛國的心，雖然未至於回去五四運動當年的歷史背景、列強入侵、軍閥混戰的景況，但相信我們現在只能安守本分、做好自己的責任、奉公守法、做好的公民，就是貢獻國家的例子。」<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局局長徐英偉期望青少年可以回顧歷史，及多了解國家發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433525&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGniPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=3655e012\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433525&h=3d54141d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433525</a>"},{"pid":"904aab40a079daa31e2da703cd41741d615f3515","tid":2515673,"uid":307203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"德先生、賽先生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad891db768e1364b6a177ec00a3783324235608","tid":2515673,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:50:23.000Z","msg":"721運動都係鄉紳為了保衛元朗領土完整姐"},{"pid":"d745bf5fb341b316b7f0377851e8204504e65075","tid":2515673,"uid":31237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:51:18.000Z","msg":"知唔知背道而馳點用？"},{"pid":"63f5413d2b2fd9ed0a30d082f74d8d8d114700f8","tid":2515673,"uid":255162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904aab40a079daa31e2da703cd41741d615f3515","tid":2515673,"uid":307203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"德先生、賽先生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly"},{"pid":"903ca50bfece59c8008c051129aa619267fed187","tid":2515673,"uid":22422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:51:59.000Z","msg":"咁宜家梁唐青儀同佢啲仔女係乜嘢國籍？"},{"pid":"4d180eb8b01977c66c73470b4cda19adbed8176f","tid":2515673,"uid":383914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"齊陰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae574df9bf2e24524519c8bd1e9f965750bf50f","tid":2515673,"uid":41411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"大家對國家既理解唔同姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8c81766d4541854491b7b17640d227a1905643","tid":2515673,"uid":110892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"904aab40a079daa31e2da703cd41741d615f3515","tid":2515673,"uid":307203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"德先生、賽先生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"賽先生有啊<br />\n德先生就唔知啦"},{"pid":"f50b49a4570ec8422ee0cbe5525e924b25d1b692","tid":2515673,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"背道而馳？<br />\n而家中共就真係背道而馳<br />\n仲衰過當年班軍閥"},{"pid":"7698c0e4cbce9acfda2362df483f6b743ed9ebad","tid":2515673,"uid":274871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:55:18.000Z","msg":"五四 反國民政府 = 愛國行為<br />\n前年 反港共政府 = 分裂國家<br />\n歷史永遠係由勝利者觀點出發"},{"pid":"542fa69921990b486951626571bda410ea328047","tid":2515673,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"904aab40a079daa31e2da703cd41741d615f3515","tid":2515673,"uid":307203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"德先生、賽先生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"而家有譚德賽先生"},{"pid":"9a0b8cac6a54e169fbdc772db127055c0f96a271","tid":2515673,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8c81766d4541854491b7b17640d227a1905643","tid":2515673,"uid":110892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"904aab40a079daa31e2da703cd41741d615f3515","tid":2515673,"uid":307203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"德先生、賽先生呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"賽先生有啊<br />\n德先生就唔知啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"其實都幾懷疑賽先生係咪都失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如科學嘅思維方式、認識方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41751f2b8f3f8cadf6066c518eac6730bbaccc91","tid":2515673,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"打輸仗割地俾人，已經唔係你領土，仲講乜撚國家完整"}]}